info.name: Sunrise - API v1
info.description:
Access our powerful credit risk assessment reports either by inputting only the company number letting our platform does the rest, including sourcing all the inputs; or manually inputting the company financials. We recommend usage if you have access to the latest unpublished financials, proprietary information or need to run sensitivity analysis.

Available in Synchronous (real time) or Asynchronous (batch) modes.

To use these scripts import the Sunrise - API v1 Environment and set the username and password variables with the right values.
